{
  "stem": "10359.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I tried-- through him and some other people-- they took out some documents from high school, Polish documents, of some sons of the offic-- Polish officers who fled to Poland when the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were more or less my age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So on the basis of their birth certificate and school things, they made for me false papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The the name that I assumed is actually an actual name of a-- of a-- of a man who was my age, who going to school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But his parents were in the army, they left when the Soviets came.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Did you know him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they-- Dorothy too was based-- her documents are based on papers which are factual papers of birth certificates and high school records and so forth.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to pay for it, naturally, with gold coins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But nobody-- first of all, people had an idea that nothing will happen, that maybe this is just a passing thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything will get organized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They wouldn't kill everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They already killed everybody, so they'll let those people go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I figured, just in case, let me make some papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I was the only one, I think-- I think the only one in Ostrog who did it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I also tried through some friends to establish some points of escape in case of something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now I had a-- my friend that we went to high school together, but he was in the lower grade.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I was teaching him German and, and Latin, and I was very close to his family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the other friend that we formed that group in high school, the jazz singing group, they helped me a lot later on after I escaped.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
